welcome_message_body: "Welcome to Seekonk, a charming town known for its scenic beauty and friendly locals. We hope you enjoy your stay and have a wonderful time exploring all that our city has to offer."

terminals.name: Main Terminal
terminals.description: The main terminal at T. F. Green Airport houses all check-in counters, baggage claim, and security checkpoints.

terminals.name: Concourse A
terminals.description: Concourse A at T. F. Green Airport serves domestic flights and includes a variety of amenities such as shops, restaurants, and a lounge.

terminals.name: Concourse B
terminals.description: Concourse B at T. F. Green Airport serves international flights and offers a range of services including duty-free shopping and dining options.

wifi.note: Complimentary WiFi is available throughout the airport.
